-    now is i2c.
+  - compatible: Should be "solomon,<chip>fb-<bus>". The only supported bus for
+    now is i2c, and the supported chips are ssd1306 and ssd1307.
   - reg: Should contain address of the controller on the I2C bus. Most likely
